HEADWORD: Prairial
<hw>Prai`ri`al"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr.
<ets>prairie</ets> meadow.]</ety> <def>The ninth month of the French
Republican calendar, which dated from September 22, 1792. It began May,
20, and ended June 18. See <er>Vendemiaire</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

